CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772399158
OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FIt is now down to the UK's Justice
OL,6,FSecretary, David Lammy, to give the
OL,7,Fbill Royal Assent.
OL,9,FDepending on how long that process
OL,10,Ftakes, the first assisted death could
OL,11,Fbe as soon as next summer, according
OL,12,Fto Jersey's Health Minister, Deputy
OL,13,FTom Binet - who says it is a "world-
OL,14,Fclass assisted dying law".
OL,16,FThe law will go further than similar
OL,17,Flegislation that is being discussed
OL,18,Facross the UK, as eligible terminally
OL,19,Fill Jersey residents will be able to
OL,20,Fhave their life ended by a willing
OL,21,Fhealthcare professional.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
