OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772399158
OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FIt follows Jersey States' historic
OL,6,Fdecision in May 2024 to approve the
OL,7,Fintroduction of an assisted dying law
OL,8,Fin principle.
OL,10,FThis allowed lawmakers to create draft
OL,11,Flegislation, which was published in
OL,12,FSeptember 2025.
OL,14,FAfter several months of delay,
OL,15,Fscrutiny, and public consultation, the
OL,16,Ffirst reading of the island's Assisted
OL,17,FDying Bill was passed on Wednesday 21
OL,18,FJanuary 2026 - with 32 votes for and
OL,19,F14 against.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
