OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FLorna Pirozzolo has incurable breast
OL,6,Fcancer and says she is pleased she
OL,7,Fwill get to choose how she dies.
OL,9,FShe explains: "It really is going to
OL,10,Fbe an option for me. I will likely be
OL,11,Fhere when the law comes in, so that is
OL,12,Fa real relief for me."
OL,14,FWhat happens now?
OL,16,FJersey is a Crown Dependency, so it
OL,17,Fsits outside of the UK with its own
OL,18,FGovernment and laws.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
