CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772399158
OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FHowever, as the island's
OL,6,Fconstitutional relationship is with
OL,7,Fthe British Monarch, any new
OL,8,Flegislation still has to receive Royal
OL,9,FAssent before it formally becomes law.
OL,11,FThe UK Justice Secretary is
OL,12,Fresponsible for reviewing and
OL,13,Fprocessing these bills and will have
OL,14,Fthe final sign-off.
OL,16,FAnother Crown Dependency, the Isle of
OL,17,FMan, became the first place in the
OL,18,FBritish Isles to pass its own Assisted
OL,19,FDying Bill in March 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
