OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FThis legislation is still awaiting the
OL,6,Fsame Royal Assent, although Jersey
OL,7,Fpoliticians say they are confident
OL,8,Ftheir bill will pass in good time.
OL,10,FThere are also differences between the
OL,11,Ftwo bills - Jersey has different
OL,12,Fresidency requirements, meaning
OL,13,Fsomeone could live on the island for a
OL,14,Fshorter amount of time before being
OL,15,Feligible for an assisted death, if
OL,16,Fthey meet the rest of the criteria.
OL,18,FWho will be eligible for an assisted
OL,19,Fdeath in Jersey?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
