CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772399158
OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FHow will the assisted death be
OL,6,Fdelivered?
OL,8,FThe lethal dose can either be self-
OL,9,Fadministered or delivered by a willing
OL,10,Fmedical professional.
OL,12,FOptions for how to take the approved
OL,13,Fdrugs include swallowing and receiving
OL,14,Fan injection.
OL,16,FA Care Plan will be completed by the
OL,17,Fadministering practitioner and the
OL,18,Findividual, which will set out where
OL,19,Fand how the assisted death will be
OL,20,Fcarried out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
