FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772399158
OL,3,CJersey votes to legalise assisted dying
OL,5,FThe administering practitioner will be
OL,6,Fa doctor or registered nurse who
OL,7,Fsupports the individual to develop
OL,8,Ftheir Assisted Dying Care Plan, and
OL,9,Fhelps them to either self-administer
OL,10,Fthe approved drugs or give them
OL,11,Fdirectly, and stays with the
OL,12,Findividual during their death.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
